---
title: Crunchy Thai Chili-Lime Chicken Salad with Peanuts, Scallions & Cilantro
description: Get ready for all the Thai flavors you love in a 10-minute salad! First you’ll make a sweet, hot, and tangy chili-lime dressing to toss with crisp lettuce, scallions, and carrots. Top with bite-size pieces of juicy fully cooked chicken, then drizzle on more dressing, sprinkle with peanuts, cilantro, and a squeeze of lime, and dig right in! After lunch, you’ll be left feeling satisfied—not overstuffed—and with the slightest spicy tingle on the tongue to remember it by.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crunchy-thai-chili-lime-chicken-salad-ff9655b9.jpg
